{"tid":926750,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京拉麵沾麵討論區","createTime":"2018-12-03T16:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T14:12:22.000Z","uid":25882,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ba74e12d4304687ed58de0366ac719dd45f8f11c","tid":926750,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:21:49.000Z","msg":"有無成日去東京嘅朋友<br />\n一齊開心share下有咩好食嘅拉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拋個磚出黎先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9jep6Nh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9jep6Nh.png&h=276f6345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMensho Tokyo<br />\n後楽園<br />\n羊肉湯底沾麵，All Topping<br />\n1080円<br />\n<br />\n講到沾麵<br />\n東京大部分都係用大量魚粉整到好咸嘅沾汁或者係大勝軒式偏酸嘅沾汁<br />\n呢間就比較特別<br />\n佢都係偏咸個邊但個汁會有都幾強嘅羊肉香味<br />\n而近年嘅新拉麵都偏向出有口感同埋紅肉嘅叉燒<br />\n呢間都唔例外<br />\n價錢黎講1080yen all topping唔算太貴<br />\n最緊要係呢間就算排隊都唔洗排太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n位置佢離東京巨蛋大約5分鐘路程<br />\n臨去睇波或者睇演唱會前去食就啱哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ae8a07e6282824ffa94d2ff29b127bbff8a035","tid":926750,"uid":172042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:06:21.000Z","msg":"關東圈內得唔得？覺得飯田商店個麵好勁"},{"pid":"488f8acf6a330163b100ef725c13bacec25c4187","tid":926750,"uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T01:54:11.000Z","msg":"秋葉原肉汁麵"},{"pid":"63b84918a347e94acc72602197ab6ff3a934163e","tid":926750,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0ae8a07e6282824ffa94d2ff29b127bbff8a035","tid":926750,"uid":172042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:06:21.000Z","msg":"關東圈內得唔得？覺得飯田商店個麵好勁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"飯田我見啲人好早去拎籌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爸打等左幾耐"},{"pid":"0bd91c3be87b377b5081cd8459f2777ceaea5512","tid":926750,"uid":162895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:51:24.000Z","msg":"留一留名先, 一個人去東京試唔同既拉麵係我最近期既目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b9f17fdcda35b941af0407a192aa8681a90f15","tid":926750,"uid":88841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:16:48.000Z","msg":"東京沾麵道冇人講？"},{"pid":"9a1c2e7dec9c49294cb71f16adcdd6ea0f04587e","tid":926750,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5b9f17fdcda35b941af0407a192aa8681a90f15","tid":926750,"uid":88841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:16:48.000Z","msg":"東京沾麵道冇人講？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:25:32.000Z","msg":"巴打識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n道係我心目中東京沾麵第一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係個店主近排成日顧佢間豬骨麵舖唔做沾麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得罪講句佢間豬骨麵真係唔算出色好心佢專心做道啦<br />\n<br />\n講開佢以前嘅徒弟近排係千葉縣開士間沾麵店叫長男もんたいちお<br />\n個湯同道好似不愧係徒弟<br />\n條隊都短過道<br />\n麵身比道硬我自己就唔太鍾意<br />\n如果鍾意硬身麵又唔想排太長嘅可以一試"},{"pid":"94469aa9d8cbcc82ac236592461ff7a1d85f079c","tid":926750,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"新宿有間食蝦湯沾麵都正，名後補"},{"pid":"08c761c1f7e3ceedb81fcc0d7651d7991107247a","tid":926750,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a67aa27fc615a148326b1ea9814ea81cd1b845","tid":926750,"uid":121443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94469aa9d8cbcc82ac236592461ff7a1d85f079c","tid":926750,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"新宿有間食蝦湯沾麵都正，名後補"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:40:36.000Z","msg":"五ノ神?"},{"pid":"4656d02ac080f510531d0e6ab92ff23ee7d26df2","tid":92675