es/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爸打等左幾耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:02:47.000Z","msg":"閒日凌晨機四點幾到羽田搭頭班京急去品川轉JR<br />\n七點九左右到門口等八點派籌，食十二點嗰輪<br />\n<br />\n不過閒日朝早可以睇佢twitter當日下晝幾點開放walk-in先去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:27:58.000Z","msg":"8點鐘去都要食12點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係等佢出event去食算數"},{"pid":"0ed0aca6c75ee4d1f9213239bfd746d880ed348c","tid":926750,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4656d02ac080f510531d0e6ab92ff23ee7d26df2","tid":926750,"uid":53563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba74e12d4304687ed58de0366ac719dd45f8f11c","tid":926750,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:21:49.000Z","msg":"有無成日去東京嘅朋友<br />\n一齊開心share下有咩好食嘅拉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拋個磚出黎先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9jep6Nh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9jep6Nh.png&h=276f6345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMensho Tokyo<br />\n後楽園<br />\n羊肉湯底沾麵，All Topping<br />\n1080円<br />\n<br />\n講到沾麵<br />\n東京大部分都係用大量魚粉整到好咸嘅沾汁或者係大勝軒式偏酸嘅沾汁<br />\n呢間就比較特別<br />\n佢都係偏咸個邊但個汁會有都幾強嘅羊肉香味<br />\n而近年嘅新拉麵都偏向出有口感同埋紅肉嘅叉燒<br />\n呢間都唔例外<br />\n價錢黎講1080yen all topping唔算太貴<br />\n最緊要係呢間就算排隊都唔洗排太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n位置佢離東京巨蛋大約5分鐘路程<br />\n臨去睇波或者睇演唱會前去食就啱哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:01:24.000Z","msg":"呢間定MENSHO本店嘅沾麵正啲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:31:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢間正啲<br />\n其實Mensho group整體黎講我覺得唔算十分出息<br />\n例如佢其中一個最新嘅brand mensho San Francisco 真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附上Mensho SF嘅圖一張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fW4Nsdm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfW4Nsdm.png&h=eccb2dbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee0597b52610d29ab669e8728fb2a69a204740f8","tid":926750,"uid":42007,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c200edbc4044f0e3b088542b2b286268a731224f","tid":926750,"uid":25882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74a67aa27fc615a148326b1ea9814ea81cd1b845","tid":926750,"uid":121443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94469aa9d8cbcc82ac236592461ff7a1d85f079c","tid":926750,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"新宿有間食蝦湯沾麵都正，名後補"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:40:36.000Z","msg":"五ノ神?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"五ノ神雖然出左名之後無以前咁好食但係蝦湯黎講仲係好出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過因為地點太好嘅關係排到傻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4HSCPsz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4HSCPsz.png&h=343236bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同brand另一間係都內嘅拉麵五ノ神水産<br />\n主打銀鱈魚湯底<br />\n係五ノ神拉麵執左之後做埋蝦湯拉麵<br />\n不過都係魚湯好食啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日去左食Lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLORTU8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLORTU8.png&h=092798da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2400d568a1f5679dcb938fc78349c093eec98a50","tid":926750,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08c761c1f7e3ceedb81fcc0d7651d7991107247a","tid":926750,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"係唔係得幾個位無售票機個間？"},{"pid":"bfda2931102bd768aa2da3184e006b0c89ca3854","tid":926750,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4b33cb5c6de0980b70bbc45fadb62b0fc0de4f4","tid":926750,"uid":145148,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"一燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:40:17.000Z","msg":"一燈由佢擴展海外市場就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早兩個月去過一次<br />\n雖然係關東圈內都仲係出色<br />\n但同以前比差左好撚多<br />\n仲有我覺得佢大部分brand都係伏黎（例如沾麵一燈）<br />\n唔會再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b13a9ae80469e82b8d50f22e462eb4d212d3d2","tid":926750,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee0597b52610d29ab669e8728fb2a69a204740f8","tid":926750,"uid":42007,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"淨係認到第三張係真鯛拉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無得開估？<br />\n仲有巴打覺得邊個最好食"},{"pid":"a369df1a4b214f23fdeeb4eec0972a8d53053c0a","tid":926750,"uid":53563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92b13a9ae80469e82b8d50f22e462eb4d212d3d2","tid":926750,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee0597b52610d29ab669e8728fb2a69a204740f8","tid":926750,"uid":42007,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"淨係認到第三張係真鯛拉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無得開估？<br />\n仲有巴打覺得邊個最好食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:46:44.000Z","msg":"第一張唔知<br />\n麥苗<br />\n真鯛<br />\n響喜<br />\n金色不如歸<br />\n應該係？"},{"pid":"34adea4a673ae679fc37dc054265856a765036bc","tid":926750,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92b13a9ae80469e82b8